Title: Publisher Correction: Capturing variation impact on molecular interactions in the IMEx Consortium mutations data set (Nature Communications, (2019), 10, 1, (10), 10.1038/s41467-018-07709-6)
Abstract: © 2019, The Author(s).In the original HTML version of this Article, the order of authors within the author list was incorrect. The IMEx Consortium contributing authors were incorrectly listed as the last author and should have been listed as the first author. This error has been corrected in the HTML version of the Article; the PDF version was correct at the time of publication.
